	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was expecting something around Fixed vs RGB vs HSL etc. 
<br />
<br />I like to work with fixed palettes, you have your limits set and you got to work within them, you can just do anything right away without being able to worry too much as there's too little to cause any significant headache.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


